{"title":"我俩出去巡逻","authors":["峭石"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我俩出去巡逻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓浓夜色如铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风涌着云朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端着乌亮的枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我俩出去巡逻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，肩膀靠着肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，后脚跟着前脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过密密的蔗林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过松软的沙窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，侧着耳朵静听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，瞪大眼睛搜索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静听每一丝风声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜索每一丛草窠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步轻得像朵云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛亮得像烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撞不响沉睡的芭蕉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊不跳唱歌的蝈蝈！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一个黎明姗姗降临，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我俩心里充满了快乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他吹起调皮的口哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我唱起心爱的军歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热情地说一声：“再见！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两双手紧紧地相握；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，我回军营去报告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他跳上渔船吹起海螺！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}